<p>In a revise [of <hi rend="italic">Birds</hi>] CD has altered "<hi rend="italic">Colaptes Chilensis</hi> Vigors" to "<hi rend="italic">Chrysoptilus Chilensis</hi> G. R. Gray". Is that right?</p> 
